snippet.title: Age of Zombies - The Story of Barry Steakfries
snippet.description:
Click to Subscribe: http://bit.ly/HalfbrickYTSubscribe

Follow us on Social Media: 
Twitter: @Halfbrick
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/halfbrick/

Barry Steakfries fans unite! 

This is the montage you have been waiting for - the origin story of Barry in all its glory! Here we have chronicled his adventures in Jetpack Joyride and Monster Dash, and how he arrived ready to battle the undead in Age of Zombies.

We're celebrating the latest update to Age of Zombies, available now worldwide with controller support and new content including rides on the legendary Zombie T-Rex!

Download on the App Store: http://bit.ly/Tfw4kt

Get it on Google Play:  http://bit.ly/1owcA4R

Available at Amazon Appstore: http://amzn.to/TftStd
